reviews.review_text: Good Taping Job! Much better then the existing Aud. I'll see how this sounds on my Paradigms this evening.

Great sound, thanks! Thanks for preserving this show in such fine sound.  This gives the listener a clear, "you are there" sensation that the soundboard cannot convey. 

One minor glitch - there's a cut in Bird Song at the 9:31 mark, just as they start playing the closing riff.  It cuts right into Weir's "we'll be back..." announcement.   That minor issue aside, it's a fantastic recording of one of their best shows of the era.  Highly recommended.
